Lemo mikwayogo Nyasaye mondo okel kue Jerusalem


1  Ne abedo mamor kane ji owachona niya,

“Wadhiuru e od Ruoth Nyasaye.”


2  Koro eri wachung’ e dhorangeyene, yaye Jerusalem.


3  Jerusalem noger mondo obed dala

ma ji chokoree gi kue kaachiel.


4  Dhout Israel biroe,

ee, jo-Ruoth Nyasaye biroe,

mondo ogone erokamano kaka nochikogi.


5  Kanyo ema nitie ut ng’ado bura,

ma ruoth ma nyakwar Daudi ng’adoe bura ni joge.


6  Lemuru mondo Jerusalem obed gi kue, kuwacho niya,

“Joma oheri, A Jerusalem, mondo odhi nyime maber.


7  Kue onego obed e ohinga mari,

kendo dongruok maber bende obed e ut jodongi.”


8  Awacho e nying owetena gi osiepena niya, “A Jerusalem, kue obed kodi.


9  Alemo ni mondo idhi nyime maber,

nikech duong’ mar od Ruoth Nyasachwa.”

